{"_id":"74Lbfavchi8y3ZHE","name":"Passive: Superposition","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/light/orb-container-orange.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":0},"description":"<p>You have a <strong><span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\">QUANTUM DOUBLE</span></strong>, an intangible copy of your Drive. It has its own Speed (tracked separately), <strong>ignores all Impact and effects</strong>, and starts each encounter Matched to you.</p>\n<p>Whenever you <strong>Boost</strong>, your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>QUANTUM DOUBLE</strong></span> can <strong>Boost</strong> instead, and when you attack with a Projected weapon or use its <strong>Pattern Trait</strong>, you can treat your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>QUANTUM DOUBLE</strong></span> as the origin for the effect.</p>\n<p>When you <strong>Zero Out</strong>, your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>QUANTUM DOUBLE</strong></span> dissipates. If you <strong>Rally</strong>, it rematerializes Matched to you.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7RsHKh5fc7D95AWk","name":"Passive: Antimatter Shell","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-blue-purple.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>At the start of your turn, you can take 1 <strong>Drive Stress</strong> to create an <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>ANTIMATTER SHELL</strong></span> around your or an allyʼs Drive. The shell lasts until its target takes any Impact &mdash; then it detonates, reducing the Impact by 1 and dealing 3 Harm to a Matched foe. You can create any number of <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>ANTIMATTER SHELLS</strong></span>, but their effects donʼt stack.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9AxxiH8qMP6AoNSA","name":"Passive: Gravity Well","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/lightning/barrier-shield-crackling-orb-pink.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>At the start of each of your turns, you can take 2 <strong>Drive Stress</strong> to activate your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>GRAVITY WELL</strong></span> this round. While active, you gain +2 <strong>Weight</strong> and are <strong>Slowed</strong>, Matched allies gain +1 <strong>Weight</strong>, and Matched foes are <strong>Locked</strong>.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EehQunMlEwaCwyS1","name":"Passive: Superfluidity","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/water/orb-water-transparent.webp","data":{"useResource":true,"resource":{"name":"Flow","value":""},"description":"<p>Whenever you <strong>Boost 2 or more</strong>, gain 1 <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>FLOW</strong></span>, up to 6. Your Projected weapons deal +1 Harm for every 2 <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>FLOW</strong></span> you have. Lose all <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>FLOW</strong></span> whenever you take <strong>Drive Burn</strong> or end your turn without <strong>Boosting</strong>.</p>\n<p>When you would lose Speed, you may spend any amount of <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>FLOW</strong></span> instead to reduce the amount lost, one-to-one.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Or9CTgDlVKVJjo1W","name":"Passive: Heaven's Eye","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-tendrils-web-purple.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Your Ranged weapons gain +1 die and deal <strong>triple</strong> Harm on Crits.</p>\n<p>Once per turn after you roll to attack, you can take any amount of <strong>Drive Stress</strong> to reroll that many dice.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"W3x73GKn6WVNQHFW","name":"Passive: Red Giant","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/earth/orb-ringed-lava-black-orange.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>On your very first turn each combat, enter <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RED GIANT STANCE</strong></span> until the start of your next turn. While in <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RED GIANT STANCE</strong></span>, you gain +2 <strong>Accel</strong>, and your Projected weapons gain +1 Harm and <strong>Decel</strong> +2.</p>\n<p>Once you exit <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RED GIANT STANCE</strong></span>, you canʼt enter it again until a full round has passed.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XI6vSl7Gs73IZHPc","name":"Passive: Entropic Harvest","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/nature/leaf-drip-light-green.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Whenever a foe is destroyed, clear 1 <strong>Drive Stress</strong>. You donʼt clear any <strong>Drive Stress</strong> for closing a Veil Breach.</p>\n<p>Whenever the GM rolls to open Veil Breaches, they roll 2d6 per foe destroyed and <strong>you</strong> pick either result.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"d4Sc5Mjb2egdZuLm","name":"Passive: Equilibrium","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/symbols/cog-shield-white-blue.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Whenever you take <strong>Drive Stress</strong>, you gain that much <strong>Inertia</strong>. This stacks with other sources of <strong>Inertia</strong>.</p>\n<p>At the end your turn, Matched allies gain half your current <strong>Inertia</strong>, rounded up.&nbsp;</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dfR3PeYftA65942g","name":"Passive: Radiance","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-beam-impact-silhouette.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":0},"description":"<p>Your Projected weapons apply <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> on hit. Foes with <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> take 1 Harm at the end of each round, and continue to burn even if you <strong>Zero Out</strong> or otherwise leave the encounter.</p>\n<p>When a foe with <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> is destroyed, they explode, applying <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> to all foes Matched to them</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gtxBTrpBL2LIHH57","name":"Passive: Sunkiller Blades","type":"section","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-axe-red.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Your Projected Melee weapons deal +1 Harm <strong>for each Status</strong> on the target, including special Statuses.</p>\n<p>At the start of your turn, you may <strong>Prime</strong> or <strong>Slow</strong> a Leading (2) foe until the start of your next turn.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ngA66WsNRu5F8UFO","name":"Passive: Oracle Sequencing","type":"section","img":"icons/skills/targeting/crosshair-arrowhead-blue.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Whenever you hit with a Projected weapon, you can choose to deal 0 Harm and <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>SEQUENCE</strong></span> all targets until the end of the encounter instead. <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>SEQUENCED</strong></span> foes are permanently <strong>Primed</strong>.</p>\n<p>When you use a power, you can choose to target <strong>any number</strong> of <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>SEQUENCED</strong></span> foes instead of that powerʼs usual target, ignoring Band requirements and taking the powerʼs <strong>Drive Stress</strong> again for each target beyond the first.&nbsp;</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"p5zLG6nHGBnsoHJD","name":"Passive: Veilborn","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/air/wind-vortex-swirl-blue-purple.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>As long as youʼre Matched to one or more active Veil Breaches, your Projected melee weapons gain +2 Harm and <strong>Overwhelm</strong>, and you gain 2 <strong>Inertia</strong> at the start of your turn.</p>\n<p>Whenever you destroy a foe, you may open a Veil Breach at the targetʼs Speed.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
